A video has emerged of the killing of three policemen by Nigerian soldiers. The policemen who according to the soldiers were thought to be Kidnappers were actually on a sanctioned mission which led to the capturing of a notorious Kidnapper in Taraba state.. Since the incident, the police and army has been going back and forth with accusations and counter accusations. In the latest version of the event, the police has asked the army to produce the alleged ‘kidnap victim’ Alhaji Hamisu Bala Wadume they claim to have rescued. See the video below: